      heading: 'Your anxiety is trying to <em>tell you something.</em>',
      lead: 'Anxiety is exhausting to live with — especially when you can’t figure out what it’s actually about. It shows up uninvited, doesn’t respond to logic, and makes everything feel more uncertain. But anxiety is a signal. And signals, when we learn to read them, have something worth hearing.',
